#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-fluent-reader-zones-support.md:1
msgid "FLUENT Reader handles zones"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-fluent-reader-zones-support.md:3
msgid ""
"The FLUENT .msh reader now handles zones and provides the user with one "
"block per defined zone. BREAKING_CHANGE: Some of the vtkFLUENTReader member "
"variables have been moved to private visibility which could impact classes "
"that inherit it and directly access member variables. BREAKING_CHANGE: Some "
"zones from the file were previously ignored by the reader, and are now "
"provided as blocks in a vktMultiBlockDataset. Users might need to filter the "
"excess out manually"
msgstr ""
